{"title":"可恶的电梯","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":0,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-6308","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一栋大楼有n层。</p><p>某天，这栋楼来了n-1个人，他们分别要去2~n楼。可是大楼的电梯坏了，只能在其中某一层停下（别问我为什么）。所以他们不得不走路（除了其中运气好的一个，也就是要去的那层刚好是电梯停下的）</p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">所以他们把楼主打了一顿</span><br></p><p>人们可以选择坐电梯，然后走路，也可以直接走路。已知：每个人上一层楼会产生x份不满意，下一层楼会产生y份不满意。问：电梯应停在那一层，才能使所有人不满意的总份数最小？</p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>输入包括三个整数，分别是n，x，y，中间以空格隔开，含义如题。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>输出有两个整数，即电梯停在的楼数和总的最小不满意数。<br/></p><p><br/></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>33 3 1</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>27 316</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1&lt;=n&lt;=10000</p><p>1&lt;=x,y&lt;=1000000000</p><p><br></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}